headline.print_headline: Saints Edge Eagles 26-24 in NFC Wild-Card Game
headline.main: Saints Edge Eagles 26-24 in NFC Wild-Card Game

lead_paragraph: The New Orleans Saints finally came up with the right plan for outdoor playoff football in cold weather. It got them their first postseason road victory.
